# 1. Outlook Exchange Setup 5.5.4.scpt
# 2. OutlookExchangeSetupLaunchAgent.sh
# 3. net.talkingmoose.OutlookExchangeSetupLaunchAgent.plist
# 4. com.microsoft.Outlook.plist for creating a configuraiton profile
